<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79c68b55-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s1828"><num value="1828">§ 1828.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to issue such rules and regulations as he deems necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
